Bad Wolf Ltd is a television [[production company]] founded by [[Julie Gardner]] and [[Jane Tranter]] in 2015 based in [[Cardiff]], [[Wales]], [[United Kingdom]].<ref name="UKCompaniesHouse">{{cite web|title=BAD WOLF LTD|url=https://beta.companieshouse.gov.uk/company/09686683/|publisher=Companies House|access-date=22 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bad Wolf Cardiff Creative|url=https://www.creativecardiff.org.uk/users/badwolf|publisher=Cardiff Creative|access-date=22 December 2019}}</ref> The company is responsible for the television series [[The Night Of]], Beddgelert, [[A Discovery of Witches (TV series)|A Discovery of Witches]], [[His Dark Materials (TV series)|His Dark Materials]] and the upcoming era of [[Doctor Who]].
